# business-hours-system

The business hours restriction system implements access control for game session creation during standard business hours (9 AM - 5 PM EST, Monday-Friday).

## Core Components

### Time Restriction Logic
- Standard business hours enforcement: 9 AM - 5 PM EST, Monday-Friday
- Allows joining existing sessions during restricted hours
- Blocks creation of new game sessions during business hours
- Importance Score: 85

### Admin Bypass System
- Session-based bypass mechanism for administrators
- Requires two-factor authentication using TOTP codes
- Admin privileges persist until explicit logout
- Importance Score: 80

### 2FA Integration
- TOTP-based authentication for admin bypass
- 30-second expiration window for generated codes
- Initial setup requires QR code scanning or manual secret key entry
- No server-side storage of TOTP codes
- Importance Score: 75

### Business Rules
1. Session Creation
   - Blocked during business hours for regular users
   - Allowed 24/7 for authenticated admins
   - Importance Score: 90

2. Session Joining
   - Allowed during all hours
   - No restrictions on existing session access
   - Importance Score: 70

3. Admin Authentication Flow
   - Admin password verification
   - Valid TOTP code requirement
   - Session-based privilege maintenance
   - Importance Score: 85

